{"tid":865504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★地鐵壞車】上班族打唔切卡 老闆出警告信:「冇得原諒」","createTime":"2018-10-17T06:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T12:21:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":311,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"487c6ed4f396a4e3d25e260d821b3094681fb31a","tid":865504,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:29:50.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】<br />\n打工仔為求準時返工，昨日已出盡法寶，由鐵路轉戰路面，甚至成為「步兵」，但面對人車爭路，處處塞爆，不少打工仔被迫遲到數小時。有網民在網上哭訴今次交通事故令他失去勤工假；亦有網民說連同昨日的遲到，今年是第二次遲到，老闆稱要<span style=\"color: red;\">出警告信，「冇得原諒」</span>，對此大感無奈；亦有網民指已提早出門，但由上水抵達鰂魚涌花上三小時，最終仍遲到十分鐘，又指近日已經因為粉嶺站有人跳軌令列車服務暫停，遲到一次，連同今次，月內已第二次遲到，擔心飯碗不保。<br />\n<br />\n勞聯主席林振昇表示，暫未收到有會員因遲到而被剋扣工錢的求助，該會會繼續跟進，又呼籲僱主應體諒今次罕見情況，不要處罰遲到員工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20181017/00176_007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181017%2F00176_007.html&d=1Xpqqb4N39bP%2FPKbGsMeAl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0d2f2814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20181017/00176_007.html</a>"},{"pid":"4fbf9fa4857ed62fcc418464903559fccd13dcf1","tid":865504,"uid":19454,"like":387,"dislike":1,"score":386,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:30:08.000Z","msg":"出警告信，「冇得原諒」<br />\n出警告信，「冇得原諒」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d0121bea0c9e8b023964d8ee180fe18522c643","tid":865504,"uid":3171,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"呼籲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5276d9af0a81a2648d7ef964f4c8b201abf34fac","tid":865504,"uid":19454,"like":375,"dislike":3,"score":372,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice